text: Chatakonda is a census town in Khammam district in the state of telangana, India. ==Geography== Chatakonda is located at .Falling Rain Genomics, Inc - Chatakonda It has an average elevation of 70 metres (229 feet). ==Demographics== India census, Chatakonda had a population of 8701. Males constitute 50% of the population and females 50%. Chatakonda has an average literacy rate of 55%, lower than the national average of 59.5%; with male literacy of 62% and female literacy of 48%. 13% of the population is under age six. ==References== Category:Cities and towns in Khammam district
